summary: Just an save game of Commander Shepard.
descriptionHtml:
Commander Shepard comes to skyrim! Game is just after exiting from the cave at start. Went with Imperials but that does not matter at this point:) 
Screenshots are taken with Sharpshooters Enb so could look different without it.

Here some mods you will need to get same look!:

High Res Face Maps for Men by Geonox: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4141

Covereyes: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4869

HQ Beards - vanilla texture replacers:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21620/?tab=3&navtag=%2Fajax%2Fmodimages%2F%3Fuser%3D0%26id%3D21620

Optional(only body):	
Better males - Beautiful nudes and faces - New hairstyles: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488

I\'m not 100% sure of all mods that it uses. Cos almost all my mods are for Female only and not sure if this uses some of contents of them:D  So please let me know that if there is a problem or he doesnt look at all same:)

Installation: Just drop on your saved games directory
